      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm trying to plan out a route for one of our delivery drivers. We've got 12 different drop-off locations in the metro area that need to be hit in a single loop to save on gas. Can you explain the best way to calculate the most efficient path so we aren't crisscrossing the city?",
